        {
            "title": "傳恒大物業最快月底前讓潛在買家提要約 作價或較現股價有折讓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">《彭博》引述知情人士指，中國恒大清盤人最快或於月底前，讓有興趣收購恒大物業(06666)的潛在買家提出要約。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"恒大物業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/06666-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"恒大物業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/06666-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">恒大物業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上述知情人士估計，潛在買家提出的要約作價，或較恒大物業現時股價有折讓。該股今日反覆偏軟，截至下午3時49分逆市跌0.78%，報1.27元，市值137.3億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報道又指，有私募基金正考慮是否提出要約，另有至少有1家廣東省國企亦正考慮收購恒大物業的可能性；若獲得滿意的收購，交易有機會在年中前達成。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15616170-%e5%82%b3%e6%81%92%e5%a4%a7%e7%89%a9%e6%a5%ad%e6%9c%80%e5%bf%ab%e6%9c%88%e5%ba%95%e5%89%8d%e8%ae%93%e6%bd%9b%e5%9c%a8%e8%b2%b7%e5%ae%b6%e6%8f%90%e8%a6%81%e7%b4%84-%e4%bd%9c%e5%83%b9%e6%88%96%e8%bc%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/06666-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 15:57:43",
